title: Commercial property market value in the United Kingdom ( UK ) 2012 to 2016
summary: Overall Market value in billion GBP has increased over the Year.
Market value in billion GBP is roughly constant from 2012 to 2013, and lastly slightly increasing from 2013 to 2015.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 2014 and 2015.
The highest Market value in billion GBP, of value 926.0 was reached at Year 2015
Minimum Market value in billion GBP about 650.0 was reached at Year 2012
